text: With the massive success of Kendall and Kylie Jenner ’ s limited - edition DropOne this year, it ’ s not surprising that the “ Keeping ” sisters are back with a second capsule collection. After teasing the range on social media, DropTwo finally dropped yesterday at 12 p. m. If you ’ re going to shop the collection, you ’ re going to want to get on it fast, as there are only 100 creations of each item. According to E! News, the reality star ’ s range covers everything from basic bodysuits and graphic tees to athleisure wear, as well as jeans with grommet cutouts, embroidered skirts, phone cases and the ultimate range of bodycon dresses.
